data.description: This adorable 2 story end unit Townhome is just walking distance to Clay Elementary School and a fun new park/playground!  This townhome features a large living room area with a gas fireplace, eat in dining area and a spacious kitchen! Laundry is on the main level next to the half bath.  As you walk up to the upper level you will find a large space to fit any of your needs such as office/toy room.  2 large bedrooms with walk in closets with one full bath and a 3/4 bath with shower! Attached 2 car garage and a beautiful open patio overlooking quality residential homes nearby.
